This time, the study is based on the actual Dragon Quest games (specifically Dragon Quest IV/Dragon Warrior IV.)

The king has given you a quest to defeat the Metal King Slime. You will be bringing Charizard along. You will be in Pokémon battles, except you are battling Slimes instead of Pokémon. Charizard can also give you hints. }
