{ You enter the Zenithian Castle. You see some Elves inside!
King of Zenithian Castle: "The Metal King Slime invaded our castle! We were just living peacefully until it attacked. It now sits in my throne room, and we cannot go near it or it will attack us. We are peaceful people; therefore we cannot fight the monster."
You: "I'm here to defeat the Metal King Slime and restore peace to your country. Do not worry; I will take care of it."
King: "Thank you! As I said earlier, the Slime is in the throne room. Please be careful!"
You set off towards the throne room for the decisive final battle of your quest. }
